title: ARCHIVED: San Francisco Vaccine Access Points
description: Update Jan 26, 2023: This dataset is no longer being updated. Please visit https://sf.gov/get-vaccinated-against-covid-19 for information on vaccine locations. A. SUMMARY Dataset contains Vaccine Access points in City and County of San Francisco as listed on https://sf.gov/vaccine-sites. This site list is not inclusive of all City Sites, as some mobile sites and other providers may not be included. B. HOW THE DATASET IS CREATED Maintained by City staff. C. UPDATE PROCESS Updated daily via automated process
